title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 7/19 - Pat Micheletti
description: Pat Micheletti joins the show to talk about the Wild's offseason, Cody McLeod, & much more.  Plus, Nordo reacts to a report that the Wolves trade for Rudy Gobert has some teams around the league upset.
